  </h3>
  <div class="trac-ticket-buttons">
  </div>
    <div class="comment searchable">
      <p>
I think there needs to be more control around what values the model should allow for blank, Since PositveInteger inherits from Integer-&gt;Field it just uses the Field clean which uses blank=<em>.    <br />
</em></p>
<p>
I think here the ORM abstraction leaks a bit.  The Database could define one set of values it will treats as blank for a given column while the django ORM has a different another for the field.<br />
</p>

    </div>

              </div>
